    "attributes": {
        "action": "Inquiry into the DVLA\u2019s performance during the Covi-19 pandemic",
        "additional_details": "Delays such as a 6 month wait for a medical restricted licence to be reissued are completely unacceptable.",
        "background": "In my view the DVLA are not fit-for-purpose. An inquiry needs to be held into their performance during the pandemic. This should lead to more efficient customer service, treatment of those with medical issues, and more.",
